About Puthiya Thalaimurai TV

 Puthiya Thalaimurai TV (Tamil: புதிய தலைமுறை டிவி) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on August 24, 2011.Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favour or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organisation or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
 
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of week end programmes.
 
The channel is promoted by Chennai based New Gen Media Corporation. The company also publishes popular Tamil magazines- Puthiya Thalaimurai and Kalvi.

Presenting the official video of Zihaal e Miskin - the heartbreak song of the season. Featuring Rohit Zinjurke and Nimrit Ahluwalia, this melody has been sung by Vishal Mishra & Shreya Ghoshal, music by Javed-Mohsin And lyrics by Kunaal Vermaa.

#ZihaaleMiskin #RohitZinjurke #NimritKaurAhluwalia  

Create reels on Zihaal e Miskin : https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/605950694837426/

🎧 Spotify : https://open.spotify.com/track/51DEaelXeJJ6cFFYbX8Hal 
🎧 JioSaavn : https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/zihaal-e-miskin/OQAgUxlXTmM

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 07 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 29th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 08 Teaser - 29th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 08 Teaser - 29th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya
Zainab Qayoom as Samiya
Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

#EhraameJunoon 
#NeelamMuneer 
#ImranAbbas

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3783 - 29 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3783: Do Do Rishte
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak ultimately succeeds in getting a leave of absence from work, but his manager is still interested in Pyaarelal's tale. Taarak explains to his boss why Pyaarelal, a.k.a. Popatlal, has been single and how being single has made his life miserable. Taarak's manager understands and gives him permission to go a little early. When Pyaarelal learns that his friend Taarak is returning, he is delighted. Champaklal is one of the elderly people, thus the Gokuldham women and Pyaarelel thought to invite him to the meeting. Pyaarelal receives a call later about another marriage proposal, but the bride's family prefers his original name, Popatlal. Now, what will he do?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3783, 29 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 47 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 24th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap

Ekam confronts Nehmat and forces the truth out of her. He blames Jasmine for ruining his life and vows to exact his revenge on her. Meanwhile, Renuka overhears Sartaj's conversation with the doctor and promises to keep Nehmat's pregnancy a secret. Will she keep her word?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
snippet.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single ‘Like A Sufi’, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

He’s accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

localized.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
localized.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single ‘Like A Sufi’, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

He’s accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Harvesting Vegetables from the Garden in Tamil | காய்கறி அறுவடை | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me in our garden for harvesting some vegetables and fruits. We really like growing plants and it is very relaxing. We have some annual vegetables, fruit trees and berry bushes. Alandra also has a lot of fun picking fruits directly from the tree. I highly encourage everybody to try gardening and grow something beautiful. Plants only need light, water, air and patience.

#steffiulagam #steffivlogsintamil #steffigardentour

Friends, hope you will grow some plants at your house too. I wish you all the best and happy gardening!

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 699 & 700 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 699 & 700 | Recap

Ekam gets perplexed after recalling the events surrounding his marriage to Nehmat. He then becomes suspicious and decides to find out the truth with the assistance of Nehmat. Will Ekam be successful this time?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3782 - 27 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3782: Rishta Aa Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal, or Pyaarelal, receives a phone call from Anjali, who informs him that she has wonderful news concerning his marriage. Pyaarelal hurries to meet Anjali at Gokuldham Society. When he arrives at Anjali's residence, he notices that other Gokuldham females are present. Anjali informs him about her cousin Nanda Kaki, who has a niece named Sapna and is looking for a groom. Pyaarelal is ecstatic after hearing the news and wants to see Sapna and her family right away. Anjali informs Pyaarelal that Sapna and her family will come at 5 in the evening. Pyaarelal now persuades Taarak to attend the gathering, but Taarak informs him that his boss may not grant him an early leave owing to work pressure.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3782, 27 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

About The Show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

दिव्या ने 2022 की यूपीएससी परीक्षा में 105वीं रैंक हासिल की है। इन्होंने दृष्टि संस्थान में जो मॉक इंटरव्यू दिया था उसे दृष्टि आई.ए.एस चैनल पर अपलोड किया गया है। हम इस उपलब्धि पर दिव्या को हार्दिक बधाई देते हैं। हम उनकी इस सुंदर यात्रा का हिस्सा बनकर बेहद खुशी महसूस कर रहे हैं और एक बार फिर हम उनके उज्ज्वल भविष्य के लिये उन्हें शुभकामनाएँ देते हैं। 
हम सभी जानते हैं कि मॉक इंटरव्यू संघ लोक सेवा आयोग द्वारा आयोजित व्यक्तित्व परीक्षण (Personality Test) के विभिन्न आयामों को समझने का एक अच्छा माध्यम है। ये मॉक इंटरव्यू न केवल उम्मीदवारों को यूपीएससी साक्षात्कार की वास्तविक प्रक्रिया से परिचित कराते हैं, बल्कि उन क्षेत्रों की पहचान करने में भी मदद करते हैं जिन पर उम्मीदवार को मेहनत करने की आवश्यकता होती है। आप चाहें तो यूपीएससी साक्षात्कार में खुद की कल्पना कर सकते हैं। साथ ही, हम दृढ़ता से अनुशंसा करते हैं कि आप इन मॉक इंटरव्यूज को देखें और आईएएस टॉपर्स के अनुभवों से सीखें ताकि जब आप परीक्षा के साक्षात्कार चरण में पहुँचें, तो आप अपना सर्वश्रेष्ठ प्रदर्शन कर सकें। 
हम आशा करते हैं कि यूपीएससी आईएएस मॉक इंटरव्यू का यह वीडियो आपको यह समझने में मदद करेगा कि पैनल के सदस्यों द्वारा पूछे गए विभिन्न प्रकार के प्रश्नों से निपटने के लिए आपको क्या दृष्टिकोण अपनाना चाहिए।

Sartaj takes Nehmat to his house and clashes with Naaz and Jasmine, who try to stop him. Meanwhile, Ekam meets Nimmo and attempts to strike up a conversation with her to learn the truth about Nehmat. Will he be able to uncover the truth?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?
